         "key": "China is a wonderful country",

         "trn": "Zhōng guó shì gè měi lì de guó jiā.",

         "val": "中国是个美丽的国家。"

      }, {

         "key": "What do you do for a living?",

         "trn": "Nǐ shì gàn shén me de?",

         "val": "你是干什么的？"

